List of cameras from which is seen on the current frame.
First per-pixel light added this frame.
Process octree raycast. May be called from a worker thread.
Update before octree reinsertion. Is called from a worker thread.
Calculate distance and prepare batches for rendering. May be called from worker thread(s), possibly re-entrantly.
Return whether a geometry update is necessary, and if it can happen in a worker thread.
Return the geometry for a specific LOD level.
Return number of occlusion geometry triangles.
Draw to occlusion buffer. Return true if did not run out of triangles.
Visualize the component as debug geometry.

detaileddescription.para: Set view mask. Is and'ed with camera's view mask to see if the object should be rendered. BIND_AS_PROPERTY
Set light mask. Is and'ed with light's and zone's light mask to see if the object should be lit. BIND_AS_PROPERTY
Set shadow mask. Is and'ed with light's light mask and zone's shadow mask to see if the object should be rendered to a shadow map. BIND_AS_PROPERTY
Set zone mask. Is and'ed with zone's zone mask to see if the object should belong to the zone. BIND_AS_PROPERTY
Set maximum number of per-pixel lights. Default 0 is unlimited. BIND_AS_PROPERTY

briefdescription.para: Mark for update and octree reinsertion. Update is automatically queued when the drawable's scene node moves or changes scale.

detaileddescription.para: Return local space bounding box. May not be applicable or properly updated on all drawables. BIND_AS_PROPERTY
Return maximum number of per-pixel lights. BIND_AS_PROPERTY
Return whether is in view this frame from any viewport camera. Excludes shadow map cameras. BIND_AS_PROPERTY

briefdescription.para: Return whether is in view of a specific camera this frame. Pass in a null camera to allow any camera, including shadow map cameras.
Set new zone. Zone assignment may optionally be temporary, meaning it needs to be re-evaluated on the next frame.
Mark in view. Also clear the light list.
Mark in view without specifying a camera. Used for shadow casters.
Sort and limit per-pixel lights to maximum allowed. Convert extra lights into vertex lights.
Sort and limit per-vertex lights to maximum allowed.
Set base pass flag for a batch.
Return whether current zone is inconclusive or dirty due to the drawable moving.
Return LOD scaled distance from camera.
Return whether is in view on the current frame. Called by View.
Return whether has a base pass.
Return the first added per-pixel light.
Add a per-pixel light affecting the object this frame.
Add a per-vertex light affecting the object this frame.
